# GrantGenius Venture Scoring

## Team Analysis

The AI Venture Grid Lab team has analyzed the GrantGenius venture opportunity across all 7 dimensions:

### 1. Market Size: 8/10
- $20B grant writing industry is substantial with clear TAM
- Multiple high-value target segments (university researchers, biotech startups, climate tech, non-profits)
- ARPU of $50K is attractive and validates premium positioning
- Market segments have distinct needs and willingness to pay

### 2. Pain Level: 9/10
- Researchers spending 40-80 hours per proposal is extremely painful
- $5K-20K per grant for professional writers is significant cost
- 10-20% success rates indicate high failure cost
- Clear ROI proposition: time + money saved

### 3. AI Advantage: 7/10
- AI can analyze winning grants to extract patterns
- Automated narrative generation adds real value
- Compliance checking reduces errors
- AI-assisted revisions improve feedback loop
- Still needs human oversight for quality assurance

### 4. Defensibility: 6/10
- Grant consultants can adopt AI tools
- Data on successful proposals creates network effects
- Agency-specific knowledge builds moat
- Moderate defensibility - human element remains important

### 5. Founder-Market Fit: 7/10
- Can validate quickly with academic networks
- Target users are accessible in research communities
- Generalist can learn grant requirements in 8 weeks
- User feedback cycles are fast in research environment

### 6. Speed to Revenue: 8/10
- SaaS model allows immediate monetization
- Clear value proposition enables quick adoption
- Tiered pricing (basic, premium, enterprise) accelerates revenue
- Can generate first dollars within months

### 7. Viral Potential: 8/10
- Research communities are tightly connected
- Success stories spread quickly in academia
- Non-profits share best practices readily
- Network effects through grant agency relationships

## Final Score: 7.6/10
- Weighted average based on venture grid methodology
- Strong market validation and pain point targeting
- Good AI application with clear value proposition

## Recommendation: GO
- Clear market need with substantial pain points
- AI creates genuine value beyond existing solutions
- Strong revenue potential with $50K ARPU
- Can achieve product-market fit relatively quickly
- Network effects and community spread create growth potential

The venture has significant upside potential while manageable execution risks.